These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: grey, white, fuchsia, blood-red, light-blue, aquamarine
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the russian is between the person who likes aquamarine and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person who likes white##1
9. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Color           | grey | white | aquamarine | light-blue | blood-red    | fuchsia  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

