.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, scientific, animation, superhero, time-travel, horror
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching family movies##2
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | horror | time-travel | superhero | animation | family  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

