.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: drama, disaster, satire, action, thriller, documentary
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, taxi, tram, van
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching action movies and the person driving the helicopter##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | drama | documentary      | thriller | action | satire      |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | van  | helicopter | taxi   | tram       | quad-bike |

