.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, grey, pink, purple, yellow, red
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes grey##1
5. the person who likes black is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the person who likes red##2
7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes red##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Color        | grey    | red | pink | black | yellow | purple   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

