2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
5. the cottage house is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the art-deco house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | satire    | western | family | drama | sports   |
| House         | palace | ranch-style | cottage | art-deco | gothic-revival  | tower |

