.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: folk, r&b, salsa, techno, metal, indie
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of indie##1
8. the fan of salsa is between the fan of techno and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Music-Genre    | folk | indie | metal  | techno      | salsa | r&b  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

