.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, video-games, camping, collecting, reading
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, indie, jazz, trance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the person who's hobby is camping is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Hobby           | camping | reading | collecting | video-games | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

