.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, singing, sudoku
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, punk, house, folk, pop, disco
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of folk##1
 2. the fan of funk is between the person who's hobby is chess and the fan of disco##2
 3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 6. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Music-Genre   | punk | funk | disco    | pop | folk | house |

