.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, drama, family, horror, satire
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff, prince, game, bolivar, oliveros
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
8. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching family movies and the dannemann-smoker##2
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | satire | family   | comedy | documentary | horror |
| Cigar           | dannemann  | game   | prince | aristoff | oliveros       | bolivar |

