.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, hedgehog, rabbit, snake
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, thriller, comedy, martial-arts, fantasy, mystery
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching family movies##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the person watching family movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | fantasy  | comedy | family      | martial-arts | mystery        |

