.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, nurse, software-developer, teacher, videographer, writer
6 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, monopoly, domino, chess, go
 1. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing go##1
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the nurse is the person playing domino##1
 4. the software-developer is between the teacher and the person playing go##2
 5. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing go and the videographer##2
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the nurse is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the bartender##1
 9. the person playing go is the bartender##1
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Job           | nurse      | teacher | software-developer | bartender   | writer  | videographer |
| Game   | domino | backgammon  | billiard             | go | monopoly | chess       |

