.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, november, april, september, august, october
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, photographer, pilot, scientist, security-guard
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the security-guard is between the scientist and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 3. the scientist is between the person who's birthday is in october and the dancer##2
 4. the photographer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the photographer and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is the paramedic##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the pilot is on the right of the paramedic##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Birthday   | september     | june | august   | april     | october       | november       |
| Job    | paramedic | pilot   | dancer | scientist | security-guard | photographer |

