 1. the person who growstulip is the indian##1
 2. the japanese is on the right of the polish##1
 3. the german is between the malaysian and the indian##2
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsiris is the german##1
 6. the person who growslily is the malaysian##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the polish##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Flower   | tulip | iris    | lily     | aconite      | dahlia    | begonia |
| Nationality   | indian | german | malaysian | indonesian | polish | japanese  |

