.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-16::.
There 6 different types of food: peach, lime, onion, pear, corn, grapefruit
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, skiing, snowboarding, swimming, volleyball
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person eating lime##2
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Food   | corn   | peach   | onion        | lime   | grapefruit        | pear   |
| Sport      | biathlon | swimming | snowboarding | skiing | volleyball | cricket |

