.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, cooking, drawing, rock-climbing, woodworking
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, soy-milk, mirinda, juice, hot-chocolate
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | drawing | camping | collecting | woodworking | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Beverage   | milk | juice | soy-milk      | mirinda     | hot-chocolate       | cola |

 